quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,"Si kammu oon fettii."
  82,2,"Si ko koode ɗe cariima."
  82,3,"Si ko maaje ɗe puccitaama."
  82,4,"Si genaale ɗeen mbaylaama."
  82,5,"Fittaandu annda kondu ardin'no e golle e kondu leelnuno e golle."
  82,6,"Ehey ma neɗɗaŋke hol ko hoomtuma e joom ma tedduɓɗo o."
  82,7,"oon takɗo ma o fotndi terɗe ma o waɗ ma potandirɗo."
  82,8,"E kala mba'adi ndi o haaja o feewnir ma."
  82,9,"Ala woni ko on yeddooɓe ñalngu noɓdi."
  82,10,"Pellet ina woodi e dow mon maleykaaji deenooji."
  82,11,"Tedduɗi binndooji (golle.)"
  82,12,"Hiɗi nganndi ko ngolloton."
  82,13,"Pellet ɓeen ɗigguɓe heɓe e ne'emaaji."
  82,14,"Faajireeɓe noon ina e yiite (jahiim.)"
  82,15,"Heɓe naatange ñande ñangu njoɓdi."
  82,16,"Ɓe ngona wirnatooɓe nge haa abada."
  82,17,"Holko anndinat ma ñalngu njobdi."
  82,18,"Refti holko anndinat ma ñalngu njobdi."
  82,19,"ñande fittaandu jogantaaka fittaandu hay hu'unde hu'unde fof ko Alla woodani ñande heen."
